        <h3>Project flow</h3>
        
        <p>To query and use one or many of the available datasets, you will have
        to perform a series of sequential requests, which all run inside a
        project.</p>
        
        <p>A project is a container that holds all the necessary data to
        prepare, boot and provide an enclave that contains the desired datasets.
        The project is created at the first request and then updated until one
        can successfully perform the last request: unlock and provide the
        enclave.</p>

